---
title: Mexican Chicken Stew with Black Beans and Corn
description: According to research, black beans contain as many antioxidants as blueberries and Brussel sprouts! We've added it to this Mexican stew along with some sweet corn kernels and peppers to make it extra satisfying.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-chicken-stew-73613408.jpg
